(24932, 24931, 'en', NULL, 'It was a pleasure to share with you our vision on how tailored automation and AI can increase your <b>efficiency</b> and <b>reduce your costs</b>.'),
(24933, 24931, 'es', NULL, 'Fue un placer compartir contigo nuestra visión sobre cómo la automatización a medida y la IA pueden aumentar tu <b>eficiencia</b> y <b>reducir tus costes</b>.'),
(24934, 24932, 'en', NULL, 'For us, your time is your most valuable asset. That\'s why we want to continue this conversation in a practical way:'),
